OL,7,FA former Sinn Fein press officer who
OL,8,Fhas admitted child sex offences was
OL,9,Femployed directly by Michelle O'Neill
OL,10,Fduring his time working at the
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland Assembly.
OL,13,FThe Assembly has confirmed that
OL,14,FMichael McMonagle was employed by Ms
OL,15,FO'Neill and three other Sinn Fein MLAs
OL,16,Facross two periods, when his salary
OL,17,Fwas paid for by Assembly allowances
OL,18,Fprovided from the public purse.
