OL,7,FMcMonagle was paid out of Ms O'Neill's
OL,8,Fstaffing allowance between March and
OL,9,FMay 2020, at a time when she was
OL,10,FStormont deputy First Minister.
OL,12,FParties can hire staff from Assembly
OL,13,Ffunds provided to them centrally, or
OL,14,Findividual MLAs can hire them from
OL,15,Ftheir own staffing allowances.
OL,17,FThe latest development in the
