OL,7,FStormont Speaker Edwin Poots has
OL,8,Fselected an urgent oral question for
OL,9,FMs O'Neill on the matter in the
OL,10,FAssembly on Monday.
OL,12,FLast month, McMonagle, 42, from
OL,13,FLimewood Street, Londonderry, admitted
OL,14,Fa series of offences, including
OL,15,Fattempting to incite a child to engage
OL,16,Fin sexual activity.
OL,18,FHe was first arrested in August 2021.
