OL,7,FIn a further development at the
OL,8,Fweekend, Sinn Fein acknowledged that
OL,9,Fthe BHF had contacted an HR official
OL,10,Fin Sinn Fein in August 2023 to query
OL,11,Fthe references, after media coverage
OL,12,Fof McMonagle being charged.
OL,14,FMs O'Neill has said she was not made
