OL,7,FOn Monday, in response to a media
OL,8,Fquery from the PA news agency on how
OL,9,FMcMonagle was paid, an Assembly
OL,10,Fspokesman said: "Michael McMonagle was
OL,11,Femployed jointly by former MLAs Daithi
OL,12,FMcKay and Mitchel McLaughlin in a full-
OL,13,Ftime position from 6 May 2014 to 31
OL,14,FOctober 2014."
OL,16,FThe spokesman added: "Michael
OL,17,FMcMonagle was employed by Michelle
OL,18,FO'Neill MLA from 2 March 2020 to 31
OL,19,FMay 2020 and then by Jemma Dolan MLA
OL,20,Ffrom 1 June 2020 to 8 July 2022 in a
OL,21,Ffull-time position."
